ard_shevardnadze.jpg|{{flagicon|Georgia}} [[Eduard Shevardnadze]]\nFile:President_of_Georgia_Mikheil_Saakashvili_in_Tbilisi,_March_22,_2008.jpg|{{flagicon|Georgia}} [[Mikheil Saakashvili]]\nFile:Matti Vanhanen 2017 06.jpg|{{flagicon|Finland}} [[Matti Vanhanen]] \nFile:Konstantinos Simitis 2012-01-23.jpg|{{flagicon|Greece}} [[Costas Simitis]] \nFile:Kostas Karamanlis 2007-10-18.jpg|{{flagicon|Greece}} [[Kostas Karamanlis]]\nFile:Pha01 mariavaleriabridge Orban cropped.jpg|{{flagicon|Hungary}} [[Viktor Orb\u00e1n]]\nFile:Ab vajpayee.jpg|{{flagicon|India}} [[Atal Bihari Vajpayee]]\nFile:IBSA-leaders Manmohan Singh.jpg|{{flagicon|India}} [[Manmohan Singh]]\nFile:President_Abdurrahman_Wahid_-_Indonesia.jpg|{{flagicon|Indonesia}} [[Abdurrahman Wahid]]\nFile:President Megawati Sukarnoputri - Indonesia.jpg|{{flagicon|Indonesia}} [[Megawati Sukarnoputri]]\nFile:Presiden Susilo Bambang Yudhoyono.png|{{flagicon|Indonesia}} [[Susilo Bambang Yudhoyono]]\nFile:Ali Khamenei Official photo (1989).jpg|{{flagicon|Iran}} '''[[Ali Khamenei]]'''\nFile:Mahmoud Ahmadinejad (Brazil 2009).jpg|{{flagicon|Iran}} [[Mahmoud Ahmadinejad]]\nFile:Mohammad Khatami, 30th Memorial Ceremony of Ali Shariati - 26 June 2007 (15 8603310160 L600).jpg|{{flagicon|Iran}} [[Mohammad Khatami]]\nFile:Saddam_Hussein_at_trial,_July_2004.JPEG|{{flagicon|Iraq|1991}} [[Saddam Hussein]]\nFile:Portrait_of_Nouri_al-Maliki.jpg|{{flagicon|Iraq}} [[Nouri al-Maliki]]\nFile:BertieAhernBerlin2007.jpg|{{flagicon|Ireland}} [[Bertie Ahern]]\nFile:Brian Cowen in Philadelphia.jpg|{{flagicon|Ireland}} [[Brian Cowen]]\nFile:Ehud_Barak_Face.jpg|{{flagicon|Israel}} [[Ehud Barak]]\nFile:Ariel Sharon 2001.jpg|{{flagicon|Israel}} [[Ariel Sharon]]\nFile:Benjamin Netanyahu.jpg|{{flagicon|Israel}} [[Benjamin Netanyahu]]\nFile:Ehud Olmert 2007Feb19.jpg|{{flagicon|Israel}} [[Ehud Olmert]]\nFile:King Abdullah - World Economic Forum on the Middle East Dead Sea Jordan 2007.jpg|{{flagicon|Jordan}} '''[[Abdullah II of Jordan]]'''\nFile:Nursultan Na