 of 2005|url=http://www.bfi.org.uk/sight-sound-magazine/best-films-of-2005|website=[[Sight & Sound]]|publisher=[[British Film Institute]]|accessdate=August 12, 2017}}</ref>\n| ''[[Cach\u00e9 (film)|Cach\u00e9]]''<ref>{{cite web|title=The Films Of 2006: Top Ten|url=http://old.bfi.org.uk/sightandsound/feature/49351|website=[[Sight & Sound]]|publisher=[[British Film Institute]]|accessdate=August 12, 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170812211038/http://old.bfi.org.uk/sightandsound/feature/49351|archive-date=August 12, 2017|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n| ''[[4 Months, 3 Weeks and 2 Days]]''<ref>{{cite web|title=The films of 2007|url=http://www.bfi.org.uk/sight-sound-magazine/best-films-2007|website=[[Sight & Sound]]|publisher=[[British Film Institute]]|accessdate=August 12, 2017}}</ref>\n| ''[[Hunger (2008 film)|Hunger]]''<ref>{{cite web|title=The films of 2008|url=http://www.bfi.org.uk/sight-sound-magazine/best-films-2008|website=[[Sight & Sound]]|publisher=[[British Film Institute]]|accessdate=August 12, 2017}}</ref>\n| ''[[A Prophet]]''<ref>{{cite web|title=The films of 2009|url=http://www.bfi.org.uk/sight-sound-magazine/best-films-2009|website=[[Sight & Sound]]|publisher=[[British Film Institute]]|accessdate=August 12, 2017}}</ref>\n|}\n[[File:Avatar Flight of Passage (33825582954).jpg|260px|thumb|The highest-grossing film of the decade was ''[[Avatar (2009 film)|Avatar]]'' (2009)]]\n'''The 20 highest-grossing films of the decade are (in order from highest to lowest grossing)'''\n\n''[[Avatar (2009 film)|Avatar]]'', ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King]]'', ''[[Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Man's Chest]]'', ''[[The Dark Knight (film)|The Dark Knight]]'', ''[[Harry Potter and the Philosopher's Stone (film)|Harry Potter and the Sorcerer's Stone]]'', ''[[Pirates of the Caribbean: At World's End]]'', ''[[Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix (film)|Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix]]'', ''[[Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince (film)|Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince]]'', ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers]]'', ''[[Shrek 2]]'', ''[[Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire (film)|Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire]]'', ''[[Spider-Man 3]]'', ''[[Ice Age: Dawn of the Dinosaurs]]'', ''[[Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets (film)|Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets]]'', ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring]]'', ''[[Finding Nemo]]'', ''[[Star Wars: Episode III \u2013 Revenge of the Sith]]'', ''[[Transformers: Revenge of the Fallen]]'', ''[[Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban (film)|Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban]]'' and ''[[Shrek the Third]]''.<ref name=\"imdb.com\">[https://www.imdb.com/boxoffice/alltimegross?region=world-wide IMDb.com] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111117141416/http://www.imdb.com/boxoffice/alltimegross?region=world-wide|date=November 17, 2011 }}</ref>\n\n'''The top 15 highest-grossing [[film series]] of the decade are (in order from highest to lowest grossing)'''\n\n[[Harry Potter (film series)|''Harry Potter'' film series]], [[The Lord of the Rings (film series)|''The Lord of the Rings'' film trilogy]], ''[[Pirates of the Caribbean (film series)|Pirates of the Caribbean]]'' film series, ''[[Spider-Man in film|Spider-Man]]'' film series, ''[[Shrek (film series)|Shrek]]'' film series, ''[[Ice Age (franchise)|Ice Age]]'' film series, ''[[Transformers (film series)|Transformers]]'' film series, ''[[X-Men (film series)|X-Men]]'' film series, ''[[Batman in film|Batman]]'' film series' ''[[Batman Begins]]'' and ''[[The Dark Knight (film)|The Dark Knight]]'', ''[[Prequel trilogy|Star Wars]]'' ''[[Star Wars: Episode II \u2013 Attack of the Clones]]'' and ''[[Star Wars: Episode III \u2013 Revenge of the Sith]]'', ''[[The Da Vinci Code (film)|The Da Vinci Code]]'' and ''[[Angels & Demons (film)|Angels & Demons]]'', ''[[The Matrix (franchise)|The Matrix]]'' film series' ''[[The Matrix Reloaded]]'' and ''[[The Matrix Revolutions]]'', ''[[The Chronicles of Narnia (film series)|The Chronicles of Narnia]]'' film series, ''[[Mission: Impossible (film series)|Mission: Impossible]]'' film series' and ''[[The Mummy (franchise)|The Mummy]]'' film series.<ref name=\"imdb.com\" />\n\n=== Actors / Entertainers ===\n{{Div col|colwidth=18em}}\n* [[Amy Adams]]\n* [[Ben Affleck]]\n* [[Jessica Alba]]\n* [[Tim Allen]]\n* [[Lauren Ambrose]]\n* [[Anthony Anderson]]\n* [[Jennifer Aniston]]\n* [[Will Arnett]]\n* [[Patricia Arquette]]\n* [[Scott Bakula]]\n* [[Alec Baldwin]]\n* [[Christian Bale]]\n* [[Antonio Banderas]]\n* [[Elizabeth Banks]]\n* [[Drew Barrymore]]\n* [[Jason Bateman]]\n* [[Kate Beckinsale]]\n* [[Kristen Bell]]\n* [[Richard Belzer]]\n* [[Jon Bernthal]] \n* [[Halle Berry]]\n* [[Jessica Biel]]\n* [[Jack Black]]\n* [[Cate Blanchett]]\n* [[Alexis Bledel]]\n* [[Orlando Bloom]]\n* [[Emily Blunt]]\n* [[David Boreanaz]]\n* [[Peter Boyle]]\n* [[Zach Braff]]\n* [[Pierce Brosnan]]\n* [[Sandra Bullock]]\n* [[Gerard Butler]]\n* [[Michael Caine]]\n* [[Steve Carell]]\n* [[Drew Carey]]\n* [[Jennifer Carpenter]]\n* [[Helena Bonham Carter]]\n* [[Kim Cattrall]]\n* [[Cedric the Entertainer]]\n* [[Sarah Chalke]]\n* [[Dave Chappelle]] \n* [[Don Cheadle]]\n* [[Michael Chiklis]]\n* [[George Clooney]]\n* [[Sacha Baron Cohen]]\n* [[Stephen Colbert]]\n* [[Holly Marie Combs]]\n* [[Frances Conroy]]\n* [[Bradley Cooper]]\n* [[Kevin Costner]]\n* [[Marion Cotillard]]\n* [[Courteney Cox]]\n* [[Daniel Craig]]\n* [[Bryan Cranston]]\n* [[Terry Crews]]\n* [[Marcia Cross]]\n* [[Russell Crowe]]\n* [[Tom Cruise]]\n* [[Penelope Cruz]]\n* [[Jon Cryer]]\n* [[Ice Cube]]\n* [[Kaley Cuoco]]\n* [[Elisha Cuthbert]]\n* [[Matt Damon]]\n* [[Claire Danes]]\n* [[Jeff Daniels]]\n* [[Ted Danson]]\n* [[Larry David]]\n* [[Kristin Davis]]\n* [[Daniel Day-Lewis]]\n* [[Ellen DeGeneres]]\n* [[Benicio del Toro]]\n* [[Judi Dench]]\n* [[Robert De Niro]]\n* [[Johnny Depp]]\n* [[Laura Dern]]\n* [[Portia de Rossi]]\n* [[Emily Deschanel]]\n* [[Zooey Deschanel]]\n